	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000991_0001"/><!--pb/@n='16r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">7<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> April 
<lb/>1857</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>Can you tell 
<lb/>me of a respectable 
<lb/>house agent? I 
<lb/>think it would 
<lb/>be well if I could 
<lb/>get out of this 
<lb/>a little way so 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000991_0002"/><!--pb/@n='16v'--> 
<lb/>as to be out of the 
<lb/>way of calls - 
<lb/>the people with 
<lb/>whom we are living 
<lb/>don't behave 
<lb/>well though we 
<lb/>pay them highly<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>A small furnished 
<lb/>house for a 
<lb/>month or so any 
<lb/>where near 
<lb/>you or this 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000991_0003"/><!--pb/@n='17r'--> 
<lb/>would be an 
<lb/>improvement<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>We don<reg>'</reg>t know 
<lb/>any trustworthy 
<lb/>agent so beg 
<lb/>to trouble you 
<lb/>for information 
<lb/>merely<reg>.</reg> I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>D. Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
